dc_description_s: This data represents Public Land Survey System (PLSS) corners for Lincoln County, Wisconsin in 2020. [This dataset is a compilation of source data from Contract Remonumentation projects, Monument Records (tie sheets), existing Survey Corners maintained by the Lincoln County Surveyor, and existing GIS Coordinates used in Parcel Data compilation and mapping. This data set is a work in progress. Users of this data should check with the Contact Identified for the latest information before using.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://maps.co.lincoln.wi.us/webapps/gisportal/data.html
